{"id":129,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":99,"title":"99. Places to live","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":22,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/99-places-to-live.129/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/0-99-places-to-live.mp3","transcript":"I live in a house.\nMy house is in a town.\nMy uncle lives in an apartment building.\nHis apartment building is in a busy city.\nMy cousin lives in a dormitory in a school.\nHe shares his room with a classmate.\nMy uncle lives out in the country.\nHe lives on a farm.\nThe police caught a criminal.\nNow the criminal lives in prison.\nWhen I go to summer camp,\nI live in a tent.\nWhen my parents go on vacation, they live in a motel or a hotel.\nA motel only has one or two floors.\nA hotel usually has many floors.\nMy aunt and uncle live in a trailer.\nThey like to move around from place to place.\nMy friends live in a cottage by a lake.\nMy grandfather lives in a retirement home.\nMany people who are about the same age as he live there.\nI would like to live in a palace.\nI think you have to be a king or a queen, or a prince or a princess to live in a palace.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:56:12","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"I live in a house.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/1.mp3","time_start":1.67,"time_end":2.98},{"position":2,"content":"My house is in a town.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/2.mp3","time_start":3.16,"time_end":5.01},{"position":3,"content":"My uncle lives in an apartment building.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/3.mp3","time_start":5.35,"time_end":7.8},{"position":4,"content":"His apartment building is in a busy city.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/4.mp3","time_start":8.36,"time_end":11.01},{"position":5,"content":"My cousin lives in a dormitory in a school.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/5.mp3","time_start":11.59,"time_end":14.75},{"position":6,"content":"He shares his room with a classmate.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/6.mp3","time_start":15.38,"time_end":17.6},{"position":7,"content":"My uncle lives out in the country.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/7.mp3","time_start":18.03,"time_end":20.2},{"position":8,"content":"He lives on a farm.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/8.mp3","time_start":20.55,"time_end":21.89},{"position":9,"content":"The police caught a criminal.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/9.mp3","time_start":23.0,"time_end":24.74},{"position":10,"content":"Now the criminal lives in prison.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/10.mp3","time_start":25.01,"time_end":27.06},{"position":11,"content":"When I go to summer camp,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/11.mp3","time_start":27.41,"time_end":29.15},{"position":12,"content":"I live in a tent.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/12.mp3","time_start":29.34,"time_end":30.72},{"position":13,"content":"When my parents go on vacation, they live in a motel or a hotel.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/99-places-to-live-2019-04-07-03-53-10/13.mp3","time_start":31.32,"time_end":35.78},{"pos